&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you looking for a new challenge?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for enthusiastic and passionate Nursing Assistants to join our Bank Team.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Joining our Bank is a great way to gain clinical skills while working in a flexible way to suit your lifestyle.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking keen, motivated, flexible and enthusiastic Health Care assistance to join our multidisciplinary team. Applicants must possess good communication skills and have the ability to work as part of a team and using their own initiative. You will be able to demonstrate a positive ‘can do’ attitude despite the difficulty of any given situation, plus be able to demonstrate the ability to weigh up situations and consider the benefits and risks before clinical decisions are made.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our service encompasses both a 17 bedded Low Secure ward and 6 bedded rehabilitation ward, and involves working with male patients who have largely been transferred from other forensic settings – prisons or medium secure establishments.&lt;/p&gt;
